Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:15.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to shine on you,\Nand always like that dazzling sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:18.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will defend you\Nfrom all the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:24.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:39.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only our hearts could connect,\NI could get you to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:46.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't\Nsee it now, don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:54.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your kindness won't be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:01:01.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be carried aloft by the wind\Nto somewhere that isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:08.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll cross the sea and cross time,\Nand I know you'll blossom one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:15.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the day,\NI'll be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:22.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can watch over you\Nlike the sun for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:32.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:40.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take your eyes off\Nthe center of the wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:45.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:49.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just have to learn by\Nactually trying your hand at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.58,0:01:53.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:54.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!\NWalk faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:59.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They all seem to be\Nexcited about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:02.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's because the Summer\NSolstice Festival is coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:03.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:08.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Around here, they say you\Ncan tell how many days are left...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:12.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...until the festival by how much the\Nvillagers have loosened their collars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:21.40,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 12\NThe Summer Solstice Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:31.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The people who passed by earlier\Nwere carrying rather large torches.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:33.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What will they be used for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:37.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they'll be used when\Nthey go from house to house...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:40.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...to light the bonfires\Nduring the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:46.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see! Those were the lights\Nthat we could see from the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:50.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At court, we celebrate the Founding\NDay Festival at the spring equinox.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:54.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It commemorates the victory over\Nthe water demon by my holy ancestor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:58.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...Torugaru, and his Warriors Eight,\Nand the founding of Shin-Yogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I always wondered\Nwhy the farmers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:06.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...didn't light their\Nbonfires at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:09.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But since they're busy\Nplanting rice at the start of spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:12.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...they began doing it at the summer\Nsolstice instead. That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:22.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every year on the summer solstice,\NI would look down on the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:25.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...from the star tower with\Nthe mikado and my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:29.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fires lit at all the houses\Nwould make it look as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:33.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...the river of heaven had\Ncome down to flow across the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:38.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to\Ngo back to your old life?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:43.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't want to go back to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:49.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Chagum!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:52.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're all gonna go practice Iucha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:55.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucha? You mean the martial art?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:57.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any other Iucha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:04:00.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to practice\Nfor the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:01.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come practice with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:06.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Iucha tournament\Non the day of the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:28.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:54.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you all bowing\Nwith your eyes closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:05:00.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are the statues of\Nthe legendary Warriors Eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:03.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...who fought alongside Mikado\NTorugaru to slay the water demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:07.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you look them in the eye,\Nyou'll be struck blind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:08.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:12.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Commoners are only struck blind\Nlooking at members of the royal family...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:15.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...who are descendants of\Ntheir sacred ancestor Torugaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is he right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:20.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:26.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, no one has ever gone blind\Njust by looking at the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:29.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:34.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you saying that you've\Nactually looked at one of the royal family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I only meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You over there, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:48.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The mighty Yarsam is about to start\Npracticing for the Iucha tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:49.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...so I want you to fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you from Rota?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:54.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell by looking at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:56.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rota?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:59.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's here for the\NSummer Solstice Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:03.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever there's a festival, traveling\Nmerchants come from far and wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:05.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's a merchant's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:09.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NLet's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:14.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why should we take orders\Nfrom a drifter like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:18.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you need our help so badly,\Nbow your head and ask politely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:24.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I have to bow down\Nto a bunch of Yogo kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:26.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:30.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get him, big brother!\NMake that foreigner sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beat him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This should be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:36.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you come\Nat me with your Iucha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:39.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be using porakku,\NRota's national martial art.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:44.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, all of you\Nhave to be my minions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way am I going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:55.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First one who touches the ground\Nwith anything above the knees loses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:57.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take that! Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:19.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:24.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:27.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not so tough now, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Round and round...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:34.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:37.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:45.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing!\NThat's so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to take it that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:49.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me any of that whining.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:54.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've won, so that means\Nyou're all under my power now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:03.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you're such a bunch of losers...\NIt doesn't seem worth it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:08.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the kids in Yogo are\Nall weaklings like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:13.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that must mean the mikado of this\Ncountry must be a real weakling too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The mikado has\Nnothing to do with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:22.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take back what you said about\Nthe mikado being a weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:27.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't insult the mikado!\NWe won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:31.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you\Ntalking about, you losers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:33.44,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:37.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, you have to take back\Nwhat you said about the mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:41.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me. Why should\NI do as my own minion tells me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no minion of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:45.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Chagum!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:49.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not even my brother could beat him!\NYou don't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:58.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind fighting you,\Nbut there's no fun in fighting a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:03.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it this way then.\NI'll give you a one-day reprieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:06.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight in the tournament\Non the day of the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:11.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the off chance that I do happen\Nto lose, I'll give in to your demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:14.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, if you lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:17.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...you have to eat slugs\Nin front of everyone, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:23.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to find some\Nbig, juicy slugs for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:25.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you come\Nwith an empty stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:34.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Balsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:38.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever traveled to Rota?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:40.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I met a boy from Rota today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:46.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was big and foul-tempered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:49.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most people from Rota are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:53.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For people as large as they are,\Nthey can be surprisingly touchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Many different races call it home...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:59.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and there's a huge gap\Nbetween rich and poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:02.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why there are so many people\Nthere with high-strung personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:05.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In contrast, the Yogo\Npeople are easygoing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:08.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...which can get on\Na Rotan's nerves all the more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:20.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm supposed to fight\Nthis Rotan boy in a Iucha match.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:25.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But he uses a martial art called\Nporakku, and he's very good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:28.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think there's\Nany way that I might beat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:36.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Porakku is a martial art developed out\Nof unarmed combat on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:40.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In comparison, Iucha is just\Nan extension of farmers' horseplay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...so the odds aren't\Nreally in your favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:46.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if you just have to throw him from\Nthe ring, you do have a chance to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:47.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:52.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll need a lot of courage\Nand a little skill to pull it off, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:56.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, when is this match\Ngoing to be held?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:58.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Solstice Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:07.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to let this one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of people go to festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where there are night stalls, there\Nwill also be shady street peddlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:21.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that means that all sorts of shady\Ncharacters, people who can't normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:25.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...show their faces in broad daylight,\Nwill also be emerging from all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:29.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and I aren't\Nsupposed to still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:33.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Living the way we do here\Nwon't raise any red flags...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:36.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but at a festival, there's no\Ntelling who might be watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:41.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we need to be inconspicuous\Nand stay in the house that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:58.05,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moribito Guardian of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:12.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash up, and then let's stack up\Nthe firewood we chopped yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:16.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We might not be able to go to the festival,\Nbut we can at least light a bonfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:22.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa, you said yesterday that\NI had a chance if I only needed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:25.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...throw him from\Nthe ring, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:28.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're still thinking about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:39.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose I can tell you if you\Npromise you won't go to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:51.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum, do you know what\Nmakes the waterwheel turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:56.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's only a slow trickle\Nof water flowing past it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:58.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:13:02.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that so little water can keep\Nsuch a heavy wheel turning steadily?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:07.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because once you get\Nsomething moving, even if it's heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:11.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...you can keep it moving\Nwith just a small amount of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:15.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And once it starts moving, the heavier\Nan object is, the greater its momentum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:18.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and the easier it is\Nto keep it moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:22.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The trick is figuring out\Nhow to give it that initial kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:37.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:38.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:41.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:53.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:50.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All that firewood we chopped...\NWe're going to use almost all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:51.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:54.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:54.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And here they are.\NLight the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:55.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:01.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:05.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:07.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light the fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:18.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since we can't go to the festival,\Nlet's treat ourselves to a special meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:29.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We might run out of firewood.\NSplit a few more logs, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:31.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:06.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm next!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:20.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum, it's almost time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:28.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. He went anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:34.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would Jiguro do\Nin a situation like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:47.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You had us completely\Noutmatched this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:49.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's have\Na toast to your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:52.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew my old man was tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:56.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your friend\Ndecided not to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So do you want to\Neat these for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:00.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:02.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:11.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so now you finally\Ndecide to show your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:14.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't want to miss out\Non your slug treat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:16.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't lost just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:19.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The tournament is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the ring is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:25.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe the truth is that\Nyou're afraid to take me on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:30.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be glad to fight you\Nif you're going to talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:31.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come crying to me later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:51.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I won't draw\Nthis out. I'll just end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:55.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come and get me, slug boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:18:00.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your only asset is your size.\NYou yourself are as slow as a slug.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:04.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't all talk, hurry up\Nand show me what you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to get himself killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:09.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:12.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was going let you off\Nwith just eating a slug...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:14.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'm going\Nto make you hurt now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:28.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He did it! Chagum won!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:29.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum won!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:33.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.68,0:18:34.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was a dirty move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:37.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You left the ring. You lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:40.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what happened!\NI didn't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:43.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, take back what\Nyou said about the mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:45.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:49.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You cheated. That means\Nthe mikado is a cheater too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:51.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what we agreed on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:53.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You little bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:54.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:55.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yarsam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:19:00.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go, Son. In Iucha,\Nyou lose if you leave the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:05.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Conceding the match is the honorable\Nthing for a man of Rota to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:08.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won the tournament this year.\NHold your head high.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:12.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In this village, there are no\Nadults stronger than I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and no child is stronger than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:16.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing can change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:18.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:31.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Conceding the match\Nisn't the issue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:39.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your boy has to keep up\Nhis end of the agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:41.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Agreement? What agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:44.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know what\Nshe's talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:47.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He says he made no promise.\NPlease stop making false accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:51.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So the father gets\Nto rule on his son's disputes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:54.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the honorable thing\Nfor a man of Rota to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:20:00.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case,\Nwhy don't we parents settle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:05.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever wins is in the right,\Nand we'll abide by what that child says.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:08.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is she talking about? Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:13.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This boy doesn't have a father,\Nso I'll be the one fighting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:14.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:18.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Women are barred from\NIucha matches, but I'm a Rotan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:21.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I myself have no\Nproblem fighting you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:24.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm from Kanbal.\NWe have a deal then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, your son is\Ngoing to keep his word.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:33.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have a long talk\Nonce this is over. Wait right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:43.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to dodge\Nat the last second...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...so feel free to give it all you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:03.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get in there! Lift her off her feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:18.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:27.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Father, you went easy on her\Nbecause she's a woman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:28.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right? That's it, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:32.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is no ordinary woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.55,0:21:35.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't win by some fluke\Nor because I held back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:39.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I fought her ten times,\Nshe would win all ten matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:44.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you promised,\Nbut apologize, and be quick about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:45.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:26.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we'd been spotted, we wouldn't\Nbe able to live like this any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:27.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You understand that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:29.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:35.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was the one\Nwho made matters worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:38.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I was the one who\Nstarted it all by breaking my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:44.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that your parents\Nwould have been proud...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:48.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that you went\Nto such lengths to fight for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:13.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I sat huddled and alone, holding\Nback the tears on those nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:20.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it felt like I was about\Nto succumb to my doubts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:25.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...there you were,\Nat my side before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:32.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was none other than you\Nwho was there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:47.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I keep wishing, "I want to be strong."\NI stumble and hurt myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:56.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But because I have you to believe in,\NI can get back to my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:03.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I simply want to tell\Nmy dear one, "Thank you. "
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.24,0:24:08.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the top of my lungs,\Nagain and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:16.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I call out to my precious loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:20.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is my voice reaching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:29.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In this world that always changes,\Nhuman warmth never does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:39.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I sensed the presence\Nof the one that I hold dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:45.48,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.51,0:24:45.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone has realized\Nthat Balsa is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.48,0:24:48.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A wild beast born of\NBalsa's karma... her past deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.82,0:24:52.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time,\N"Neither Human nor Tiger."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:57.03,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 13\NNeither Human nor Tiger
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.05,0:24:56.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deep within Balsa, something\Nthat had lain dormant is roused...
